Package com.ericelsken.android.web

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExceptionHandler
    An interface that defines Exception handling throughout different parts of this library.
    RequestCallback
    Defines a callback contract used by RequestHandlers to signal the caller when events on the Request life-cycle occur.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultExceptionHandler
    This class is a simple implementation of ExceptionHandler that simply logs an Exception and returns false to indicate that the Exception was not handled, allowing for other parts of this library to handle the Exception.
    Request
    This class represents some request to be made to a remote http or https server.
    Request.Builder
    Utility class for building Request objects.
    RequestHandler
    This class handles the Request life-cycle for a given, single Request object.
    RequestManager
    This class is a Singleton implementation that manages all instances of RequestHanlders that are used by an application.
    Response
    This class represents the response or result of executing a Request.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HttpException
    A representation of an HTTP Response that has a non 2xx status code.
    RequestCancelledException
    Instances of this class indicate that a Request was cancelled before the execution completed.
    SchemeException
    Instances of this class indicate that the URI of an attempted Request have a scheme other that http or https.
